from dbd subject of right in of right in prelude to current event in i go on he the you see they overturn they kill deposition of bear employ bulk resident build microdistrict no on my wife i go to to go shop return to five in the even we into one of my the bus get to lot of people not the store well first we do know then fellow i know come up to me guy you here for go home i go on he the you see they overturn they kill he help me we get home we home for two during time of into our but the neighbor would let them in the build there be of them they stick piece of in their they be shout something but you could it it one voice or two of them be shout in chorus they turn build they go up to the third floor we see they throw thing out the window while they come out the one of in his recorder third they go on the store we to ourselves midnight on we go to hide school no which be in microdistrict there be two other there with u there be of u out of of them i only know ernest before he move to from the the school let u in first he do to but there nowhere else for u to go we to with him him into it we be tell on the there would be on our microdistrict we go to on the second floor on the city they three telephone number could be use to summon or i one of them the first of the city committee i him for i we in school no we need to be well he get it there i send out help now i know his voice the first be to our i speak with him when i he here two hour the we shout the school we look out the window to people be outside come out we here to get you they club in their the there with u where should i go i if your life be of to you you go down there the be here they leave he do he go down there the be here he i let them out the door they go point with his with shout noise the mob set off in the direction he point so the we be promise do come they send u help right of send soldier he send his own i positive do no one see u enter the school no one know we be there in we the school until seven in the morning no soldier of sort to our in the morning we go to my in microdistrict the soldier take u to the sk club from there the club with people there be lot of people of u there no one boy three month old die right in my there single doctor nothing the boy uninjured there be no wind or bruise on him he just very ill they him mouth-to-mouth they do everything they could under the but be to him his mother young couple be right there on the floor i for spot for u in the sk we child of our own i to find room or something to put my in i go up to the third floor there be lot of soldier up there with limp with their break open they be terrible sight young guy of them there be lot of too everyone be everyone cry for help i think the city committee ignore u completely true there kopek or kopek of cooky cost kopek be sell for bottle soft drink cost ruble but there no to get the thing i meet my old uncle there he me well up in his eye my whole life he tell me we be friendly people we work together he over his house now he me there nothing he could he just cry you his feel of course reference the pogrom in soviet volume i eyewitness edit by by bonner publish by d ny dbd not lesson in center for study forget the box punishment inflict on it turkish president turgut 